{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"nonisolated","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"tint","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"_","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"tint","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore5ColorV","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Color","text":"Color","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"?) -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"some","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4ViewP","text":"View","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/View","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"\n","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The tint ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Color","type":"reference"},{"text":" to apply.","type":"text"}]}],"name":"tint"}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use this method to override the default accent color for this view."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Unlike an app’s accent color, which can be overridden by user"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"preference, the tint color is always respected and should be used as a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"way to provide additional meaning to the control."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This example shows Answer and Decline buttons with "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/ShapeStyle\/green","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"t